wiki.content:
"Teeth" is a song from Lady GaGa's second studio album "The Fame Monster". The song is the eighth and final track on the album. The song's main sentence, "Show me your teeth" means, in GaGa's own words, "Show me the truth". It is written by Lady GaGa and Taja Riley.
